Installation from google code required a few alterations for the backend

1. Not done via fab. Use:
	hg archive -r Tagname -I yabi-be-twisted ~/temporary
	scp ~/temporary/yabi-be-twisted yabi@yabi:/usr/local/yabi/src/yabi-be-twisted/tag-version

2. Need to bootstrap, but from release symlink so the init script can find the correct virtualpython
	cd /usr/local/yabi/src/yabi-be-twisted
	rm release && ln -s tag-version release
	cd release
	wget http://ccg-python-build.googlecode.com/hg/bootstrap.sh
	chmod 700 bootstrap.sh
	./bootstrap.sh

3. Change initscript to use 
	TWISTDLIST="/usr/local/yabi/src/yabi-be-twisted/release/virt_release/bin/twistd"

4. Start yabibe
	/usr/local/yabi/src/yabi-be-twisted/release/init_scripts/centos/yabibe start
